{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/style-text-inputs-as-form-controls","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Formatiranje polja za unos teksta kao kontroli forme","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete dodati Font Awesome ikonu <code>fa-paper-plane</code> dodavanjem <code>&#x3C;i class=\"fa fa-paper-plane\">&#x3C;/i></code> unutar vašeg elementa za slanje (<code>button</code>).</p>\n<p>Dodajte klasu <code>form-control</code> polju za unos teksta vaše forme. Dodajte klase <code>btn btn-primary</code> na dugme za slanje vaše forme. Takođe, dodajte ovo dugme sa Font Awesome ikonom <code>fa-paper-plane</code>.</p>\n<p>Svi tekstualni elementi <code>&#x3C;input></code>, <code>&#x3C;textarea></code> i <code>&#x3C;select></code> koji imaju klasu <code>.form-control</code> moraju imati širinu od 100%.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed908845","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18312,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/style-text-inputs-as-form-controls"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\