sonality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n        <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Dugme za slanje u vašoj formi mora imati klase <code>btn btn-primary</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('button[type=\"submit\"]')?.classList?.contains('btn'));\r\nassert.isTrue(document.querySelector('button[type=\"submit\"]')?.classList?.contains('btn-primary'));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da dodate <code>&#x3C;i class=\"fa fa-paper-plane\">&#x3C;/i></code> unutar vašeg elementa za slanje (<code>button</code>).</p>","testString":"const submitButton = document.querySelector('button[type=\"submit\"]');\r\nconst fontIcon = submitButton?.querySelectorAll('i.fa.fa-paper-plane'); \r\n\r\nassert.lengthOf(fontIcon ,1);"},{"text":"<p>Polje za unos <code>input</code> u vašoj formi mora imati klasu <code>form-control</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('input[type=\"text\"]')?.classList?.contains('form-control'));"},{"text":"<p>Svaki vaš element <code>i</code> treba da ima zatvarajući label.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/i>/g);\r\nassert.lengthOf(code.match(/<\\/i/g),4);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"style-text-inputs-as-form-controls","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"bootstrap","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css